data.description: Welcome to 393 Pine Top Drive in Longleaf Estates! Tucked away on a very spacious 3.7+ Acre Lot with mature trees! Swimming Pool, Huge Metal Garage/Storage Building, Fenced Garden Area, Walk out Basement and Huge Upper Deck Area, Firepit - This property is an entertainers dream! Covered front porch leads into foyer with formal dining area to your right! Kitchen with large center island with breakfast bar and breakfast nook! Living Room with stained tongue and groove vaulted ceiling and stone fireplace. Owners Suite on Main level - large walk-in closet, soaking tub and separate shower. 2 other bedrooms and full guest bathroom on main floor. Downstairs you'll find a huge great room with another stone fireplace and wet bar area! 2 other rooms on the lower level that could be used as bedrooms 4 and 5! Above the Garage you'll find a spacious bonus room with endless uses! Freshly Painted Interior! New HVAC! New Water Lines and Tap!
